    <h1 itemprop="headline" class=" ">Donald Trump signs new travel ban executive order targeting six Muslim-majority countries</h1>

    
            <div class="intro">
                <p>Activists say countless thousands of people will be affected by the order</p>
      </div>
            <ul class="caption meta inline-pipes-list">
              <li class="author" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
          <span itemprop="name"><a href="/author/andrew-buncombe" title="Andrew Buncombe" itemprop="sameAs">Andrew Buncombe</a></span>
                      New York                  </li>
                    <li>
          <a href="https://twitter.com/AndrewBuncombe">@AndrewBuncombe</a>
        </li>
                    <li title="6 March 2017 22:25 London"><time data-microtimes='{"published":"1488817800000","display":0,"changed":"1488839116000"}' datetime="Mon, 03/06/2017 - 22:25">Monday 6 March 2017 22:25 GMT</time></li>
                    <li class="comments">
          <a href="#commentsDiv" id="comment-count" class="icon-comment"></a>
        </li>
          </ul>
    <div id="gigya-share-btns-1"></div>
        <div class="fb-like">
      <iframe src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/like.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FIndependentUS%2F&width=450&layout=button&action=like&size=large&show_faces=false&share=false&height=35&appId=235586169789578" width="70" height="35" style="border:none;overflow:hidden;float:left;" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" allowTransparency="true"></iframe>
      <div class="fb-info">Click to follow<br />The Independent US</div>
    </div>
      </header>

  
          <figure itemprop="associatedMedia video" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/VideoObject" class="featured-media medium-width">
    
